@{U}                                                                                @{UU}@{APEN 2}
¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯
@{APEN 1}@{JLEFT}
@{B}DISPLAY = OWNSCREEN | WORKBENCH [or WB]@{UB} - instructs Stratego to either open on
the WB window, or on a custom screen. Default is @{B}OwnScreen@{UB}.
@{B}AGGRESSOR = ON | OFF@{UB} - switch the starting state of
@{"Rules - Aggressor Advantage" link AggressorAdvantage}. Default is off.
@{B}RESCUE = ON | OFF@{UB} - switch the starting state of @{"Rules - Rescue" link Rescue}. Default is off.
@{B}SILENT = ON | OFF@{UB} - switch the starting state of @{"Rules - Silent Defence" link SilentDefence}.
Default is off.

@{B}GFXMODE = ECS | RTG@{UB} - will switch between 16 and 256 colour gfx when they are
ready. Default is ECS.
@{B}SOUND = ON | OFF@{UB} - switch @{B}sound@{UB} either off or on in the game. Default is on.
@{B}FOGOFWAR = ON | OFF@{UB} - switch off the random FogOfWar samples.  Only effective
if <B>SOUND</B> is not turned OFF. Default is on.

